Interface Server_Interface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Auction_RemoteService

    public interface Server_Interface
extends java.rmi.Remote
    This interface defines the behaviour of the methods that will be implemented by the remote Service
